30 bool ThetaStar::GetNext(const Point &curr, Point &next)
31 {
32  if(glPathCreated)
33  {
34  if(currPath.size() == 0)
35  {
36  next = curr;
37  return true;
38  }
39 
40  if(currPath.size() > 1)
41  {
42  float sqDistToCurr = (currPath.front() - curr).SquaredEuclideanNorm();
43  float sqDelta = options->delta * options->delta;
44  if(sqDistToCurr < sqDelta)
45  {
46  currPath.pop_front();
47  next = currPath.front();
48  return true;
49  }
50  }
51 
52  Node currNode = map->GetClosestNode(curr), nextNode = map->GetClosestNode(currPath.front());
53  if(currNode == nextNode || visChecker.checkLine(currNode.i, currNode.j, nextNode.i, nextNode.j, *map))
54  {
55  next = currPath.front();
56  return true;
57  }
58 
59  Point last = currPath.front();
60  currPath.pop_front();
61 
62  bool isLastAccessible = SearchPath(map->GetClosestNode(curr), map->GetClosestNode(last));
63  if(isLastAccessible)
64  {
65  next = currPath.front();
66  return true;
67  }
68 
69  }
70  return false;
71 }

74 bool ThetaStar::SearchPath(const Node &start, const Node &goal)
75 {
76  if(glPathCreated)
77  {
78  close.clear();
79  for(auto &l : open)
80  {
81  l.clear();
82  }
83  openSize = 0;
84  }
85  else
86  {
87  open.resize(map->GetHeight());
88  }
89 
90  Node curNode;
91  curNode.i = start.i;
92  curNode.j = start.j;
93  curNode.g = 0;
94  curNode.H = ComputeHFromCellToCell(curNode.i, curNode.j, goal.i, goal.j);
95  curNode.F = options->hweight * curNode.H;
96  curNode.parent = nullptr;
97  AddOpen(curNode);
98  int closeSize = 0;
99  bool pathfound = false;
100  while (!StopCriterion())
101  {
102  curNode = FindMin();
103  close.insert({curNode.i * map->GetWidth() + curNode.j, curNode});
104  closeSize++;
105  open[curNode.i].pop_front();
106  openSize--;
107  if (curNode == goal)
108  {
109  pathfound = true;
110  break;
111  }
112  std::list<Node> successors = FindSuccessors(curNode);
113  std::list<Node>::iterator it = successors.begin();
114  auto parent = &(close.find(curNode.i * map->GetWidth() + curNode.j)->second);
115  while (it != successors.end()) {
116  it->parent = parent;
117  it->H = ComputeHFromCellToCell(it->i, it->j, goal.i, goal.j);
118  *it = ResetParent(*it, *it->parent);
119  it->F = it->g + options->hweight * it->H;
120  AddOpen(*it);
121  it++;
122  }
123  }
124 
125  if (pathfound)
126  {
127  MakePrimaryPath(curNode);
128  }
129  return pathfound;
130 }

143 void ThetaStar::AddOpen(Node newNode)
144 {
145  std::list<Node>::iterator iter, pos;
146 
147  if (open[newNode.i].size() == 0) {
148  open[newNode.i].push_back(newNode);
149  openSize++;
150  return;
151  }
152 
153  pos = open[newNode.i].end();
154  bool posFound = false;
155  for (iter = open[newNode.i].begin(); iter != open[newNode.i].end(); ++iter)
156  {
157  if (!posFound && iter->F >= newNode.F)
158  {
159  if(iter->F == newNode.F)
160  {
161  if((options->breakingties == CN_SP_BT_GMAX && newNode.g >= iter->g)
162  || (options->breakingties == CN_SP_BT_GMIN && newNode.g <= iter->g))
163  {
164  pos = iter;
165  posFound = true;
166  }
167  }
168  else
169  {
170  pos = iter;
171  posFound = true;
172  }
173  }
174  if (iter->j == newNode.j)
175  {
176  if (newNode.F >= iter->F)
177  return;
178  else
179  {
180  if (pos == iter)
181  {
182  iter->F = newNode.F;
183  iter->g = newNode.g;
184  iter->parent = newNode.parent;
185  return;
186  }
187  open[newNode.i].erase(iter);
188  openSize--;
189  break;
190  }
191  }
192  }
193  openSize++;
194  open[newNode.i].insert(pos, newNode);
195 }

198 Node ThetaStar::FindMin()
199 {
200  Node min;
201  min.F = std::numeric_limits<double>::infinity();
202  for (int i = 0; i < open.size(); i++)
203  {
204  if(!open[i].empty() && open[i].begin()->F <= min.F)
205  {
206  if(open[i].begin()->F == min.F)
207  {
208  if((options->breakingties == CN_SP_BT_GMAX && open[i].begin()->g >= min.g)
209  || (options->breakingties == CN_SP_BT_GMIN && open[i].begin()->g <= min.g))
210  {
211  min = *open[i].begin();
212  }
213  }
214  else
215  {
216  min = *open[i].begin();
217  }
218  }
219  }
220  return min;

224 float ThetaStar::ComputeHFromCellToCell(int i1, int j1, int i2, int j2) const
225 {
226  switch (options->metrictype)
227  {
228  case CN_SP_MT_EUCL:
229  return static_cast<float>(sqrt((i2 - i1)*(i2 - i1)+(j2 - j1)*(j2 - j1)));
230  case CN_SP_MT_DIAG:
231  return static_cast<float>(abs(abs(i2 - i1) - abs(j2 - j1)) + sqrt(2) * (std::min(abs(i2 - i1),abs(j2 - j1))));
232  case CN_SP_MT_MANH:
233  return (abs(i2 - i1) + abs(j2 - j1));
234  case CN_SP_MT_CHEB:
235  return std::max(abs(i2 - i1),abs(j2 - j1));
236  default:
237  return 0;
238  }
239 }

242 Node ThetaStar::ResetParent(Node current, Node parent)
243 {
244 
245  if (parent.parent == nullptr)
246  return current;
247  if(current == *parent.parent)
248  return current;
249 
250  if (visChecker.checkLine(parent.parent->i, parent.parent->j, current.i, current.j, *map))
251  {
252  current.g = parent.parent->g + Distance(parent.parent->i, parent.parent->j, current.i, current.j);
253  current.parent = parent.parent;
254  return current;
255  }
256  return current;
257 }

280 std::list<Node> ThetaStar::FindSuccessors(Node curNode)
281 {
282  Node newNode;
283  std::list<Node> successors;
284  for (int i = -1; i <= +1; i++)
285  for (int j = -1; j <= +1; j++)
286  if ((i != 0 || j != 0) && map->CellOnGrid(curNode.i + i, curNode.j + j) &&
287  (visChecker.checkTraversability(curNode.i + i, curNode.j + j, *map)))
288  {
289  if (i != 0 && j != 0)
290  {
291  if (!options->cutcorners)
292  {
293  if (map->CellIsObstacle(curNode.i, curNode.j + j) ||
294  map->CellIsObstacle(curNode.i + i, curNode.j))
295  continue;
296  }
297  else if (!options->allowsqueeze)
298  {
299  if (map->CellIsObstacle(curNode.i, curNode.j + j) &&
300  map->CellIsObstacle(curNode.i + i, curNode.j))
301  continue;
302  }
303  }
304  if (close.find((curNode.i + i) * map->GetWidth() + curNode.j + j) == close.end())
305  {
306  newNode.i = curNode.i + i;
307  newNode.j = curNode.j + j;
308  if(i == 0 || j == 0)
309  newNode.g = curNode.g + 1;
310  else
311  newNode.g = curNode.g + sqrt(2);
312  successors.push_front(newNode);
313  }
314  }
315  return successors;
316 }
